data.description: NO HOA! NO REAR NEIGHBORS! SOLAR! PRIME LOCATION! POSSIBLE BUYER CREDIT~ Welcome home to 28385 Northmoore Place, conveniently nestled in the heart of Menifee. Perfect opportunity for first-time homebuyers or investors seeking a well-priced gem! This home offers potential for long-term improvements and appreciation! This spacious, two-story, 3 Bedroom, 2.5 bath home features three large bedrooms, an additional office nook, and a convenient separate laundry room upstairs that provides ample storage. The oversized master suite has views of the surrounding valley and features a large master bath with double sinks, separate tub & shower, and a large walk-in closet. Downstairs offers two separate family rooms,  large-open concept kitchen -  oversized island included! The large, pool-sized backyard is begging to be made into an entertainer’s dream with how much potential it has (and no rear neighbors!). The space already offers a large Alumawood patio cover with ceiling fans. The large, undeveloped yard leaves a blank slate for your ideal backyard space. Cozy up to your fireplace that warms up the large family room and kitchen area. Bring your paint-brush and vision for upgrading to make this house the perfect home for you! Conveniently located close to the local college, hospital, freeway, and shopping!
